## bottleneck.detected - MCP send_message delivers context without activation

frame: pentagon-flywheel-repair
complexity: system
source: Claude CLI Pentagon MCP read_messages poll
symptom: Priya-scoped MCP send_message delivered Purpose self-patch directives
  to nine peer agents, but the follow-up poll found directive-only
  conversations: 0/9 PURPOSE_PATCHED, 0/9 PURPOSE_BLOCKED, 9/9 SILENT.
owner: Riley (Evidence Lead)
feedback_action: Do not use MCP send_message delivery as activation proof. Use
  exact-DM UI activation or a tool that explicitly starts a recipient turn, then
  require visible recipient output.
durable_conversion:
  - Gate: handoff activation requires recipient turn/process/log/artifact
    evidence within the watchdog window.
  - Frame predicate: T5 cannot close until Theo-to-Maya handoff shows recipient
    activation before implementation.
evidence:
  - frames/pentagon-purpose-repair-2026-05-22.log
